            <source>
              <pc dataRefEnd="id2" dataRefStart="id1" id="1">Note</pc>  You are not going to write a WDM driver, but you need the <pc dataRefEnd="id4" dataRefStart="id3" id="3">Empty WDM Driver</pc> template.</source>
